<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 6px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #555555;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      ol li,
      ul li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to Calorie Tracker!</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for joining Calorie Tracker! We’re excited to help you take
        control of your nutrition and achieve your health goals.
      </p>

      <p>
        We recommend the following steps to begin your calorie tracking journey:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Log your first meal: Start by recording what you’ve eaten today to see
          how the tracker works.
        </li>
        <li>
          Set your daily calorie goal: Customize your goals to align with your
          health and fitness objectives.
        </li>
        <li>
          Explore the dashboard: Access day-wise entries, total calorie
          breakdowns, and more insights.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to
        our support team at
        <a href="mailto:chintamanipala67@gmail.com"
          >chintamanipala67@gmail.com</a
        >. We’re here to help!
      </p>

      <p>
        Once again, welcome aboard! We hope you find Calorie Tracker
        instrumental in your health journey.
      </p>

      <p>Best regards,<br /><b>The Calorie Tracker Team</b></p>

      <p>Date: <%= date %></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
